                </div>
                
                <h3>Basic Process:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>Save your Mii data to a Wii Remote</li>
                    <li>Connect the Wii Remote to a computer via Bluetooth</li>
                    <li>Use specialized software to extract the Mii data</li>
