                    This method requires technical knowledge. For detailed instructions, visit the <a href="https://github.com/Kestron06/MiiJS" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiiJS documentation</a>.
                </p>
            </section>
            
            <section id="switch-recreation" class="guide-section">
                <h2>Method 4: Manual Recreation on Switch</h2>
                
                <div class="method-overview">
                    <strong>Best for:</strong> Any system ‚Üí Switch
                    <strong>Difficulty:</strong> Easy to Moderate (depending on complexity)
                </div>
                
                <h3>Steps:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>View the original Mii (on old system or InfiniMii)</li>
                    <li>On Switch, go to <strong>System Settings</strong> ‚Üí <strong>Mii</strong></li>
                    <li>Select <strong>"Create/Edit a Mii"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"Create New"</strong></li>
                    <li>Manually recreate the Mii by matching:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Face shape and skin tone</li>
                            <li>Hair style and color</li>
                            <li>Eye shape, color, and position</li>
                            <li>Nose and mouth shape</li>
                            <li>Accessories (glasses, facial hair, etc.)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Save your recreated Mii</li>
                </ol>
                
                <div class="pro-tip">
